\s Bwana, upokee maisha yangu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Bwana, upokee maisha yangu\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Yawe yako tu kwa sikuzote\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na mikono ninakupa itumike kazi ya mapendo Kwa kukutukuza, Bwana.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Hii miguu yangu upokee ikimbie kukutumikia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na sauti ukamate kwa kuimba sifa yako, Yesu, Wewe ni Mufalme wangu.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na midomo vile itangaze\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Neno lako kwa wenye makosa\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Mali yangu yote iwe mali yako, Yesu Bwana wangu, Kwa kufanya kazi yako.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Kwa miguu yako, Bwana Yesu,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Ninatoa mwili wangu wote\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ee ninakupenda, Bwana, sikuzote ninataka sana Wewe pekee utukuzwe.\bd*
